OPERATION
	
	A pointer to a struct sembuf value
	
	struct sembuf {
	       short sem_op;
	       short sem_num;
	       short sem_flag;
	}

	
	sem_num
		the index of the semaphore you want to work on
		
	sem_op
		-1: down 1
		1: up 1

		Remember that you can do numbers other than 1 and -1
		if you put -x the semaphore must be >=x for the operation to work
